      *              * Fine controlli                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A normalizzazioni                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-600.
       cnt-tdo-nok-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazioni                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-nok-610.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero contabile bancaria                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
