           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      38                   to   v-car                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      41                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Premere un tasto per presa visione [ ]"
