           move      w-tes-ide-dat (1)    to   rf-ddp-ide-dat         .
           move      w-tes-ide-ute (1)    to   rf-ddp-ide-ute         .
           move      w-tes-ide-fas (1)    to   rf-ddp-ide-fas         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
