      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-dat-chs-999.
       det-dat-chs-180.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-dat-chs-999.
       det-dat-chs-999.
